ackground-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ဖြစ်သည်။</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">(၁) ဆီးခက်</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">(၂)<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-transform: var(--mud-typography-default-text-transform);\">ပရိတ်ကြိုး</span></div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">(၃) ပန်းမျိုးစုံ</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">(၄) သပြေညွန့်</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">(၅) အုန်းညွန့်</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">စသဖြင့်ဖြစ်ပါသည်။ အစဉ်အလာအားဖြင့် အုန်းညွှန့် (၇) ညွန့်၊</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ဆီးခက် (၇) ခက်၊ သပြေညွန့် (၇) ညွန့် စသဖြင့် ခုနှစ်ရက်သား သမီးများကို</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ရည်ညွှန်းကာ ထည့်သွင်းလေ့ရှိ၏။</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ရည်ရွယ်ချက်</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">သိကြားမင်းသည် မိုးနှင့်မိုးကြိုးကို အစိုးရသူဟု ဆိုကြ၏။ တစ်နှစ်</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ပတ်လုံး မိုးဦး၊ မိုးလယ်၊ မိုးနှောင်းကောင်းစေရန်၊ သီးနှံများ ဖြစ်ထွန်း</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ထွက်ရှိစေရန် ရည်သန်၍ သိကြားနတ်အား ပူဇော်ပသကြ၏။ သိကြားမင်း</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">သည် လူသားတို့၏ ဆင်းရဲချမ်းသာ၊ ကောင်းကျိုးဆိုးကျိုးဟူသမျှကို စီရင်သူ၊</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ကိုးကွယ်စောင်ရှောက်သူဟု ယုံကြည်ကြသည့်အလျောက် ပူဇော်ပသကြ</div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(95, 99, 104); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-align: start; background-color: rgba(241, 243, 244, 0.5);\">ခြင်း ဖြစ်ပေသည်။</div><!--EndFragment-->"
